  "content": {
    "introduction": "Add Leboncoin search result pages to scrape by providing search URLs. This scraper extracts all classified listings including phone numbers when available.\n\nThis scraper is identical to Leboncoin Listings Search Export but adds phone number extraction capabilities.",
